Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上溯至宇宙初始 周遭还只是一片漆黑{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the beginning, there was darkness.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时 忽地一声巨响{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then... Bang!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间空间以及物质皆由此发端{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Giving birth to an endless expanding existence{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}此后不断膨胀 延伸 永无止境{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}of time, space, and matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天 新的发现都在不断为我们解开{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕴藏于这里的那些神秘莫测{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the mysterious, the mind-blowing,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令人大开眼界 致命的秘密{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the deadly secrets of a place we call{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们称这个地方为"宇宙"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在深邃虚无的太空{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In the deep nothingness of space,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙的沉默被打破{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the cosmic silence is broken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太空其实很嘈杂{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Space is actually kind of a noisy place.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}星系 恒星 行星和卫星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Galaxies, stars, planets, and moons{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}高唱着奇异的外域神曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}sing out with strange and alien music.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们让人以为是外域发来传真{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They sound a little bit like an alien fax.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.47,0:00:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们将以倒数的形式{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Now the cosmic playlist{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}揭晓宇宙十大金曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a top ten countdown,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}向大家呈现宇宙最精彩的…{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the greatest hits of the universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}外域声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in a symphony of alien sounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在太空 无人能听到你的尖叫{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In space no one can hear you scream.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.36,0:01:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}作为雷德利·斯科特导演的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}As the promo line for Ridley Scott's{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.59,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}科幻电影《异形》的广告词{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}science-fiction film Alien,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它刻意地让你背脊发凉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}it was designed to send chills down your spine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.46,0:01:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它基于一个混乱的认识{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's based on the unsettling idea{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}认为太空是真空的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that space is a vacuum,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.88,0:01:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}声音 无论是尖叫 呼喊 还是唱歌{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and sounds, whether screams, shouts, or songs,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}都不能在真空里传播{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}can't travel in a vacuum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}果真如此吗？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But is that really true?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种想法太狭窄{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, it's kind of narrow to think that,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不仅在太空里 你听不到任何人的尖叫{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in space, you can't hear anyone scream,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.35,0:01:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且在地球 也有许多声音我们听不到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}because, in fact, here on Earth, there are lots of sounds we can't hear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它们或是音调太高 或是音调太低{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're either too high a pitch or too low a pitch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}再者 太空不是完全空洞的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Moreover, space isn't completely empty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}最后一点 太空的定义是什么？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then finally, you know, what's the definition of space?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}如果我是在火星表面的宇航员{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If I'm an astronaut on the surface of Mars{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿着宇航服的我 是不是在太空里？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I have a spacesuit on, am I in space, or am I not?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会认为是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Well, I would think I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}好的 就这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Okay, let's try right over here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}说回地球{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Back on Earth,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}美国加利福尼亚州{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Bruce Betts of The Planetary Society{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}帕萨迪纳行星学会的布鲁斯.贝茨{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}in Pasadena, California, has given a lot of thought{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}对火星和声音颇有研究{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to Mars and the subject of sound.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他在计算机上编写了{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}He's programmed his computer{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他命名为"火星终结者"的程序{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with what he calls the "Marsinator"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去演示在火星寒冷的二氧化碳大气层中{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to demonstrate what his voice would sound like in the cold,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在没有宇航服的情况下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}carbon-dioxide atmosphere of Mars...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他的声音是怎样的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}without those space suits.{\r}
