Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来较为低沉{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}so it sounded deeper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让我们用"火星终结者"来进行模拟{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So let's go ahead and simulate that using the Marsinator,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我会录下我的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and I will record my voice,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后让它变成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and then we will shift it{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在火星上听到的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}to what it would sound like on Mars.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我在火星上的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is what I'd sound like on Mars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我当然希望能有氧气呼吸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}although I'd be wishing I had some oxygen to breathe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}然后我通过"火星终结者"对它进行加工{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Then I go ahead and process it, put it through the Marsinator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}接着我们回放它 听一听是什么样子{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And then we play it back and see what it sounds like.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是我在火星上的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This is how I would sound on Mars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我当然希望能有氧气呼吸{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}although I'd be wishing I had some oxygen to breathe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}当然 如果真的有人在火星上这样做{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Of course, if humans ever do make it to Mars,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们不会透过大气层听到他们的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}we will not hear their voices through the atmosphere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们要依赖的是无线电波…{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Instead, we'll get them via radio waves...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种在我们身边萦绕的重要声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the way many of our most important sounds already reach us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们一想到声音 总是想起{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We're familiar with thinking of sound as something{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}穿过空气来到跟前的东西{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that comes through the air to us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正如谈话时彼此所听到的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}just like we hear each other when we're talking,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但实际上 许多我们听到的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but, in fact, a lot of the sounds that we hear{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是用电磁信号来传送的{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are transmitted through electromagnetic signals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}例如 电机是把电视信号{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For example, your television actually transmits{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}转化为声音 让你能听到{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}a television signal into sound that you can hear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}谁是今晚的第一个选手？{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Who's our first contestant tonight?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙里的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Sound in the cosmos{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}永远也不会穿过虚空直达我们这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will never reach us directly across empty space,{\r}
