Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是必不可少的载体{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}are the inevitable carriers,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从而让我们能够通过聆听{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}bringing us a universe we can hear...{\r}
