Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一开始 脉冲星发射的无线电波被探测到很有规律{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The first pulsars to be detected emitted radio waves so regular{\r}
