Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一颗缓慢转动的脉冲星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}For a slowly rotating pulsar,{\r}
