Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来象是一个音符{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that registers like a note in your ears.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}脉冲星是巨大质量的恒星坍塌的产物{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Pulsars form from the collapse of very massive stars{\r}
