Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一颗质量巨大的恒星{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But how long does it actually take{\r}
