Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这是佛罗里达州坦帕市的谢尔曼想知道的…{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}That's what Sherman D. of Tampa, Florida, wanted to...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.74,0:23:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}宇宙问题{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}ask the universe,{\r}
