Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}这种膨胀气体的话{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}the expanding gases.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.23,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可是 虽然好象是不可思议{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}But although it may seem incredible,{\r}
