Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只不过是一两秒的事{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}can take just a second or two,{\r}
