Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因核聚变而不停燃烧{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and burning by nuclear fusion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 正如下一首金曲呈现的那样{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So our home star can hardly keep quiet,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们家园的明星很不安份{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}as our next hit proves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}第七名是这首热辣的爵士金曲{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}This hot combo chimes in at number seven on the countdown.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}"太阳之歌"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Here it is, the "Song of the Sun."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.08,0:24:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太阳的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Sun makes sounds,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}不可爱{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}but they're not really sunny sounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.72,0:24:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}听起来不好受{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're not happy sounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}有点象难听的低沉咯咯声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}They're kind of low, ominous roars that gurgle along.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.53,0:24:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太阳之所以发出声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}The Sun makes sounds because there are a bunch of gases{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}是因为气流串由于对流而忽上忽下{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}going up and down through a process called convection.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.42,0:24:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}从而产生贯穿太阳这个气体球体的压力波{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So they're sending pressure waves through the ball of gas that is the Sun,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.98,0:24:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}让人听起来有点象钟声{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}and it kind of rings like a bell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.26,0:24:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}与钟声不同 太阳的声音{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Unlike a bell, the Sun rings{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}同时糅合着一千万种不同的音调{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with 10 million different tones at once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.31,0:24:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们从太阳表面压力波的微小鼓胀{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}We detect them from the tiny bulges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.46,0:24:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可以检测到它们{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from the pressure waves on the Sun's surface.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.78,0:25:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}太阳监测卫星能够对鼓胀高度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Solar satellites measure the height of the bulges{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.55,0:25:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}进行十分精确的测量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}with exquisite accuracy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.14,0:25:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}除了声音 它们还带来了科学知识{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Apart from sound, they also produce science.{\r}
